    sc "We never have enough people for it. Essentially, we take people in without even checking their number of stigmata or their status in society. The rest of the world doesn't take kindly to us because of it."


translate English day1_8a9c9878:


    sc "Since you two are still in training, though, you won't be directly sent to the pestis. Instead, you'll probably be doing simple jobs like cleaning."


translate English day1_c4d7dfce:


    nar "Securett continues to walk as he explains, his voice flat and disinterested."


translate English day1_31355341:


    nar "The cold terminology pierces my ears as I travel down the dark path."


translate English day1_bffb8445:


    nar "I'm not completely sure I have an accurate understanding of the terms and explanations I've heard."


