    nvl clear


translate English day1_c694a91a:


    nar "After traveling a bit, he stops in front of a residential building. I can see plenty of signs that people once lived there, but not a single person in sight."


translate English day1_1692543b:


    nar "As I hurry to catch up to him, my foot catches on some kind of flat board."


translate English day1_270c7b59:


    nar "There are several of them sticking out of the ground. They look like signs that are trying to keep people out."


translate English day1_132992b9:


    pl "Nobody told me about any of this beforehand..."


translate English day1_da5815fb:


    sc "Would you just be quiet for a moment?"


translate English day1_43dfb354:


    pl "Excuse me?!"


translate English day1_622ed503:


    nar "Angry at his cold complaint, my voice becomes rough. But a moment later, he smoothly passes a mask to me."


translate English day1_135d82e6:


    nar "Confused, I say nothing more, and take the mask from him."


translate English day1_cb7e5a87:


    nar "After he gives another mask to Maya, he starts rolling up his sleeves."


translate English day1_fcf9f0fa:


    sc "Breathe through your nose as little as possible."


translate English day1_76f5e758:


    "\n Securett puts on white rubber gloves that go all the way up to his elbows. Then, he puts his own mask on before taking out a relatively large bucket and a few sacks from the handcart we brought here."


translate English day1_863fca46:


    "Having lived in a harsh place where people died every day, this wasn't my first time seeing corpses. Nevertheless, the sight I witnessed once I passed through the door was a terrible one."


translate English day1_a7b9262a:


    "Maya gasps and tenses, her body shaking. I step in front of her to block the view. Even through all the white smoke from the disinfectant, I can clearly see the maggots covering the floor like a living sheet."


translate English day1_92206715:


    et "With too much exposure to moisture, the wooden floor has rotted away, and the pieces of the corpse are stuck to it--they've begun to melt, and have already turned black. Flies buzz around the crushed, desiccated skin."


translate English day1_29592ad0:


    my "Urgh..."


translate English day1_9a8131df:


    nar "Unable to breathe at the horrific sight, Maya covers her mouth and nearly falls to the ground."


translate English day1_8dfb5c84:


    nar "Her delicate arms and legs are shaking. I feel so bad for her--and also concerned over what might happen if she really did fall."


translate English day1_3fd657cf:


    my "It's awful...!"


translate English day1_33ff4cf0:


    sc "You call this awful? This is proof that this person lived. Have some respect."


translate English day1_91168c42:


    my "Urgh..."


translate English day1_20d9e3bc:


    pl "Yeah, sure, maybe, but it's just a dead body now. You're not supposed to shove stuff like this in other people's faces."


translate English day1_c45a1700:


    sc "...Well, it's also proof that this person died."


translate English day1_9fa6d43b:


    nar "Securett sighs from inside his mask and picks up a sack."


translate English day1_2df59565:


    sc "I'll handle this. Stand back."


translate English day1_01d681a7:


    sc "If you just stand there, you'll get in the way of my work."


translate English day1_f26bc177:


    nar "Is that a normal thing to say in this situation?"


translate English day1_6dd53da3:


    nar "I want to argue with him somehow, but more than that, I can't leave Maya alone."


translate English day1_ce3a771d:


    nar "Because of how stifling the air in there was, the air outside feels awfully refreshing now."


translate English day1_755b72ea:


    nar "Maya leans against me, finally putting one foot in front of the other with some steadiness."


translate English day1_b702cc60:


    nar "Eventually, the hand softly holding my shoulder squeezes tightly. She's still shaking..."


translate English day1_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day1_3c864f85:


    "\n Eventually, she lets go and heads over to the wall. Before I can think of something to say, Maya loudly vomits."


translate English day1_4d95fa27:


    "The watery, mostly uncolored contents of her stomach fall from her mouth to the floor in slick clumps.{w} She then slides down along the wall to the ground, not even a hint of color on her face."


translate English day1_a2f9e24f:


    "\"Are you alright?\" I ask, walking up to her to check on her."


translate English day1_ff543c34:


    et "She bites down on her lower lip and groans in pain as she shakes her head.{w} Her eyes are squeezed shut, and tears fall quickly from them."


translate English day1_9b512654:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I-I can't... I-I-I can't do this...!\" she weakly stammers."


translate English day1_5b5833bf:


    "\"I said I didn't want to do it! I-I didn't want to come here at all!\""


translate English day1_614a05e8:


    "\"Hey, calm down! Come on...\""


translate English day1_75d6db80:


    "I use the outside of my mask to wipe the bile from Maya's mouth a little at a time.{w} She was driven here to this polar region, and now she's raised her voice in terror. She looks so much smaller now."


translate English day1_39b4b99a:


    "Sensing my feelings, Maya sniffles and uses her own sleeve to wipe her eyes."


translate English day1_70da1700:


    "\"I wish I was in your shoes,\" she says. \"You get to go to the Magic Department once your training is over.\""


translate English day1_fa3bdb01:


    et "Despite being inarticulate through her wheezing, her words resonate clearly in my ears."


translate English day1_7194a2e2:



    nvl clear
    "\n Her eyelids are red and swollen, probably from rubbing them so much."


translate English day1_686473fc:


    "\"It's rough not having any talent...\" she goes on. \"It's really rough, [na2]. To have nowhere to go...\""


translate English day1_2c9487eb:


    "I haven't seen very many girls my age. {w}Plenty of their brothers were around where I used to live, but the sisters were either pretty young or quite a bit older than me."


translate English day1_320db4c0:


    "Because of that, I've never even seen a girl crying like this--much less had to comfort one."


translate English day1_ca997ddd:


    et "But here is one, right next to me, just one year apart. Words of consolation whirl through my head, only to shatter pointlessly the moment I try to speak."


translate English day1_0b9b7ba3:



    nvl clear    
    "\n My mind goes blank, then gives way to a certain thought."


translate English day1_48d76014:


    "Do people in the capital shove children like her out into the real world just because they've technically become adults?"


translate English day1_64c6b531:


    "\"I didn't want to become an adult at all,\""


translate English day1_e8913837:


    "she says, echoing the one question in my otherwise empty head."


translate English day1_2cea7f12:


    "We weren't prepared for this in the slightest. What were we even supposed to do?"


translate English day1_72c900b9:


    "\"Adults... Adults are the worst!\""


translate English day1_a10269c4:


    "Her hand, raised high above her, swings down as if to throw something, then lies there, trembling. I take that hand and squeeze it."


translate English day1_6a0f6af3:


    et "Her hand is much smaller than mine and is covered in tears and snot all the way to her sleeve."


translate English day1_76b2fe88_10:


    nvl clear


translate English day1_f5dab9cc:


    "\n \"Then *I'll* help you!\" I say."


translate English day1_00e54ca4:


    "Maya's eyes widen as she looks at me."


translate English day1_a7e48fed:


    "\"W-With what...?\" she asks."


translate English day1_8562e75e:


    "Her confused voice sounds a lot calmer now than before. Her ragged breathing has been steadying out, too."


translate English day1_4cb172bd:


    "\"I'll just help you,\" I repeat. \"No matter what happens--and no matter what you need help with!\""


translate English day1_2845e3bd:


    et "Maya is surprised, but I'm downright shocked. I didn't realize I'd grabbed her hand like that. I release it."


translate English day1_e8c370c1:



    nvl clear
    "\n As I do, her wide eyes slowly return to normal. That probably calmed her down a little. She looks down like she usually does, then sniffles."


translate English day1_0fef287c:


    et "\n \"Th-Thank you...\" she says."


translate English day1_76b2fe88_11:


    nvl clear


translate English day1_6d65a1cf:


    pl "U-Uh. Sorry about that."


translate English day1_21aee497:


    my "No, don't be. I'm the one who should be sorry for worrying you..."


translate English day1_446b690f:


    my "[na2]... I've thought this since the moment we met, but you really seem to like helping people."


translate English day1_ad516e3a:


    pl "From the moment we met?"


translate English day1_5bd0ceea:


    my "You don't remember...? We, um... Well, we met on the train coming here."


translate English day1_e97936e5:


    pl "Wait, really? Oh, huh. Now that you mention it..."


translate English day1_26b9ef8b:


    nar "So that's why I felt like I've seen Maya somewhere before..."


translate English day1_76b2fe88_12:


    nvl clear


translate English day1_a4321251:


    nar "We go back to the house and hear the clatter of the hand cart."


translate English day1_ffd2da3c:


    nar "The empty sacks from before are now full."


translate English day1_00120ad4:


    nar "He must have dealt with the gore inside. I glance to the side, accidentally locking eyes with him."


translate English day1_4d9e4e37:


    nar "Securett uses a dirty glove to lower his mask, then hands a mop and broom to us--one each."


translate English day1_3a1e1777:


    sc "Ever cleaned before?"


translate English day1_100a2735:


    pl "With rags, sure."


translate English day1_a34fa91e:


    sc "Then could you get the living room looking nice? I picked everything up, so..."


translate English day1_aa724d4e:


    pl "Ah, gotcha..."


translate English day1_e46c798b:


    my "......"


translate English day1_55a79978:


    sc "Don't think you can stomach it?"


translate English day1_a93c9e58:


    my "No, I'll be fine..."


translate English day1_386a4c4b:


    sc "You're only human. I won't demand a perfect job on day one."


translate English day1_3eb7791a:


    sc "But this is the easy part, so you need to at least do your best with this."


translate English day1_7480d2bb:


    my "Right..."


translate English day1_626be368:


    nar "Starting tomorrow, we'd have to get used to not only seeing dead bodies, but also to touching them."


translate English day1_1e8635e2:


    nar "But even with anxiety rising above every other emotion, seeing Maya's face twisted into even more worry than mine naturally made me want to worry about her, too."


translate English day1_b7019016:


    nar "She's never been an active conversationalist, but she's been a lot quieter than she was before."


translate English day1_3e85015e:


    nar "I would have to think over what to talk about with her carefully."


translate English day1_c5680670:


    nar "As three pairs of footfalls and the rolling of heavy hand cart reverberate around us, Securett finally breaks the silence."


translate English day1_c9dc9451:


    sc "Noon already..."


translate English day1_6d50a25b:


    pl "Huh?"


translate English day1_d6a24cfb:


    sc "This is when the temple has lunchtime. You two go back ahead of me."


translate English day1_e81b9c49:


    pl "What should we do after eating?"


translate English day1_4d9f8eba:


    sc "Hmm... I guess you should rest up, then go back to your dorms."


translate English day1_cdf6d317:


    my "Y-You're letting us go back...?"


translate English day1_4b49c67a:


    sc "We don't usually make trainees work very late. Didn't you hear about that?"


translate English day1_1c0082ae:


    my "Oh...!"


translate English day1_c0f9d814:


    pl "Good thing, too!"


translate English day1_77791284_3:


    sc "......"


translate English day1_2dc88211:


    sc "Also, starting tomorrow, could you ask those girls about work instead? I was only asked to do this for today, so..."


translate English day1_6cc96d45:


    nar "Just as I'm about to ask him more about that, he pulls the hand cart away with a loud clatter, marking the end of the conversation."


translate English day1_ac288723:


    nar "I didn't even respond to that. He probably made that loud noise on purpose."


translate English day1_9b1b621f:


    nar "What a pain. As I watch him grow smaller and smaller in the distance without bothering to turn back, I curse him under my breath in retaliation."


translate English day1_76b2fe88_13:


    nvl clear


translate English day1_eb025c70:


    "\n When Maya and I reach the cafeteria near our department, we find a lot more people around than before."


translate English day1_e83e0578:


    "People who give off similar auras are chatting and laughing about pointless things in their assigned groups.{w} As we pass them, their topics sound similar as well, yet they're all different."


translate English day1_df76e007:


    "As we enter, people we've never seen before see us and break out into laughter. {w}The laughter spreads around them in a strange rippling effect."


translate English day1_3b76cc7c:


    et "Are newbies coming back from their jobs so amusing to them? {w}Apparently, we've earned some popularity in this department."


translate English day1_3da299e4:



    nvl clear
    "\n They bombard us with greetings and questions. As we're responding to them, someone behind me softly grabs my shoulder amidst the noise of the room."


translate English day1_8dfe0f4e:


    "\"I'm borrowing him!\" she says."


translate English day1_b1802bba:


    "It's the blonde-haired girl we met this morning."


translate English day1_e82afb41:


    et "The scent of her thick perfume seems a little different to me now. Maybe she's been somewhere full of the stench of corpses this entire time."


translate English day1_46f6331c:



    nvl clear
    "\n She's been working here this whole time too. The more a girl her age wanted to doll herself up, the more she'd probably hate the stench. Even I would refuse to do this, if I had the choice."


translate English day1_e6a6cc39:


    "As she tugs on my arm, the nearby boys that had accosted me grin and wave their hands after me."


translate English day1_c75bd0e6:


    et "I'd thought maybe people in the capital would be gloomy and unsociable, but it looks like I was wrong."


translate English day1_99e2dcc9:


    pl "Thanks for getting me out of that one..."


translate English day1_797b056c:


    pl "You weren't lying when you said a lot of people would be here..."


translate English day1_e68b5b3c:


    lz2 "Ahaha! You're dead tired, huh?"


translate English day1_af0729c0:


    lz1 "Maya!"


translate English day1_9daee7f4:


    pl "And [na], too, lest you forget."


translate English day1_cd0b4336_2:


    nar "{nw}"


translate English day1_d2e4ef22:


    lz1 "Are you okay? Did this buffoon or that other annoying kid bully you or anything?"


translate English day1_922a6352:


    my "I, um..."


translate English day1_b0dc580f:


    pl "Hey, we weren't bullying her!"


translate English day1_ebb0d4d0:


    lz2 "Ahh, it's making me dizzy..."


translate English day1_ca0db380:


    lz2 " It wasn't this noisy before, so maybe it's because the sun hasn't come up lately. Everyone's talking about disasters and calamities and such."


translate English day1_e378661f:


    pl "About what?"


translate English day1_7cfd2c64:


    lz1 "Ugh, those crazy beliefs about the end of the world!"


translate English day1_7ee0edf8:


    lz1 "All this stuff about this being the 2000th year since that great disaster... I'm so sick of all these superstitious beliefs!"


translate English day1_14cc3a29:


    lz2 "Yeah, and we had so many applications for a while when all the apocalyptic rumors about the great flood were going around, too, didn't we?"


translate English day1_b5e77846:


    lz1 "And those Magic Department mooks almost worked themselves to death. Wish I could have seen them. Hee hee..."


translate English day1_3f56c578:


    lz2 "They just like rumors, that's all. Right?"


translate English day1_48948b4f:


    lz1 "Yeah, right~"


translate English day1_2fcf754f:


    lz2 "Anyway, how was work, you two? Pretty rough, yeah?"


translate English day1_d2966ea4:


    pl "It was, uh, more than I expected... Actually, I'm not sure I'm ever gonna get used to it."


translate English day1_ef06fa9b:


    lz1 "You might not ever. It's still really rough for us too."


translate English day1_6a017f9d:


    lz1 "The cardinal here was the one who set up this insane department. He's got to be touched in the head or something."


translate English day1_6883cf5d:


    nar "The sandwich I was given as my share is the worst sandwich I've ever seen."


translate English day1_5c5c2de5:


    nar "The bread is hard and cold and not only is there a complete dearth of any meat on it, the sloppily-applied sauce is like nothing I've ever seen before."


translate English day1_3d77d8e1:


    nar "To make matters even worse, the only thing sandwiched in this sandwich is a slice of lettuce, and I don't know how long it's been sitting out, but it's chewy as rubber."


translate English day1_e721e552:


    my "Is this it...?"


translate English day1_8bd0164c:


    nar "Maya says something about it before I can."


translate English day1_c56c1157:


    lz2 "There's milk, too."


translate English day1_7a7de6bd:


    pl "Wait, hang on! You're telling me this is supposed to fill me up?!"


translate English day1_c5843bc2:


    lz1 "Oh, be quiet and stop your incessant whining! You're not a child!"


translate English day1_4a51aaba:


    lz1 "Everyone here feels the same way without you making a fuss about it! So shut up and eat!"


translate English day1_1fe2afe4:


    pl "Urgh..."


translate English day1_9c80f076:


    nar "I've got a lot of complaints, but I reluctantly force my teeth to bite through the world's worst bread."


translate English day1_59f530d8:


    nar "\"Mealtime\"--though it would be blasphemous to call this food and conversation that--continued to drag on."


translate English day1_98a3a873:


    my "Umm..."


translate English day1_f8e19e93:


    lz2 "Hm?"


translate English day1_1e04a6b1:


    my "I was just wondering what Securett is like. We left early, so..."


translate English day1_21e6c907:


    lz1 "What?! Ugh, thanks for making me lose my appetite."


translate English day1_0ecedc08:


    lz1 "Maya, you don't have a thing for that sleazebag, do you?"


translate English day1_40570f46:


    my "N-No, it's not that!"


translate English day1_e706546f:


    pl "How old is he? He's pretty small... Actually, are you sure he's male?"


translate English day1_8c9c42fe:


    lz2 "He's the same age as you, and yes. He doesn't quite seem to fit in here, does he? Apparently he has three stigmata."


translate English day1_70b9061b:


    lz2 "Is that amazing? I don't know. I have three stigmata too! Most of the people here know each other, since we were raised in the same monastery, but nobody seems to have ever seen him before."


translate English day1_c30dfa3b:


    lz2 "They say he's from the capital. I wonder what he was doing before this."


translate English day1_e63f607f:


    lz1 "It's all just awful! I wouldn't want to risk catching some disease from him. Actually, maybe that's why he doesn't cling to people."


translate English day1_e79f8e2c:


    nar "Their docile expressions change completely. Is it that funny to them? I zone out, unable to keep up."


translate English day1_b5fb3f64:


    nar "Maya's face, meanwhile, is a nice contrast to mine--she still looks like she's a second away from crying, just like the first time I met her."


translate English day1_82f4c886:


    nar "Maya falls silent again. She probably doesn't know what to say either."


translate English day1_bc6d04df:


    lz2 "But apparently, Securett's been working here for a while, making him perfect to foist the more annoying jobs onto."


translate English day1_b47bff60:


    lz1 "Yeah, just like this morning. With guys like him, whoever foists the pain-in-the-butt job onto someone else first is the winner."


translate English day1_5a7ad754:


    lz1 "...Oh. Not to say you two were a pain in the butt, really. Just... You know what I'm saying, right?"


translate English day1_11699d67:


    my "So he has seniority here..."


translate English day1_0c67863d:


    pl "Not bad for someone so measly."


translate English day1_53764539:


    lz2 "You're pretty cute, Maya, so you might actually be able to draw his interest if you cling to him enough."


translate English day1_ed0166d2:


    my "I... I couldn't...!"


translate English day1_0c9d46f1:


    lz1 "Hey! Keep your weird ideas to yourself!"


translate English day1_cce3dcc6:


    lz2 "He might be into younger girls, you know. After all, men are all..."


translate English day1_76b2fe88_14:


    nvl clear


translate English day1_252f87dd:


    "\n \"...___ and ___.\""


translate English day1_bbc88237:


    "With Chairwoman right next to them, Blondie bends forward and whispers that into Maya's ears. They both go wide-eyed in surprise upon hearing it."


translate English day1_bbbd54d3:


    "Chairwoman laughs. \"Cut that out!\" she says, giving Blondie a light push on the shoulder. {w}I watch as the two of them start cackling."


translate English day1_1db8d69b:


    "She probably kept her voice down on purpose. Even with a good view of her lips moving, I couldn't make out what she said."


translate English day1_f6e84fdb:


    "\"Aha, ha...\" I laughed flatly. To be honest, I could kind of guess from context. Poor Maya; she's giving a troubled, empty smile again."


translate English day1_53800730:


    et "Idly, I wonder why they're doing this in front of me, anyway. Did they forget I'm here? That's when my eyes meet with hers as she laughs."


translate English day1_56518177:



    nvl clear
    "\n The girl, just nearby, leans on her shoulder and directs a narrow-eyed gaze at me."


translate English day1_35cca06a:


    "She doesn't laugh loudly--if anything, it's more like a titter. That's when I become sure this wasn't a coincidence or a misunderstanding. They made the joke at my expense. Is this all a warning or something?"


translate English day1_a332b77a:


    et "I don't have time to think about it any more than that, though. A bell rings in the distance, and the girls' faces shift back to their cool, serious facades."


translate English day1_ee0c6d6f:


    lz1 "Ahhh, this won't do... I have to get back to work."


translate English day1_7cd1e867:


    my "Oh. Lunchtime is over..."


translate English day1_a9dc0773:


    lz2 "Ugh, I wish I could go back to being a trainee!"


translate English day1_6d2a9508:


    pl "You're leaving?"


translate English day1_bbaf85eb:


    lz1 "Yes, and if you're not busy, I suggest taking a look around."


translate English day1_2281bf87:


    lz1 "If you don't make an effort to get used to this place, you'll start getting lost all the time. The temple is super big!"


translate English day1_0ef59f04:


    my "*sigh*..."


translate English day1_04e5f6dc:


    lz2 "See you later, little kittens!"


translate English day1_78669bec:


    pl "Right. Best of luck with your work, too!"


translate English day1_hakuB__dcb84916:


    "\n The blue-black color of the sky has blended into the air around me, making it even colder. They told me the capital was a chilly place, but I didn't think it would be this frigid."


translate English day1_hakuB__f4189811:


    "Is it night now? Or is it actually morning? The sky has been dark since this morning, so I have no way of knowing what time of day it actually is. As my surroundings rapidly darken, an uncertainty I was trying not to think about crawls up from the bottom of my mind."


translate English day1_hakuB__35cd86ad:


    "\"No, I can't... I can't be lost, can I?\""


translate English day1_hakuB__8616e4d5:


    et "I'm pretty sure I'm not very far from where I started. {w}But this deep, overgrown, unpaved path is definitely enough to scare me."


translate English day1_hakuB__15e05b47:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"That's just great...\" I say, admitting to my blunder. I scratch the back of my head. There's no point standing around like this, so I turn around to go back the way I came. But then, on the other side, I see what looks like a building."


translate English day1_hakuB__7b14d986:


    "It has huge glass windows, plus a big cylindrical tower or something. If I'm not mistaken, that's a chapel--but something seems... off about it."


translate English day1_hakuB__6bb322dd:


    et "It dominates the space around it, like some abandoned building. It's the only thing in this completely overgrown outdoor area."


translate English day1_hakuB__d23e7f9c:



    nvl clear
    "\n I approach it to check things out. Still nobody around. Through the dirty windows, I see vines growing up on the rotting walls like a monster messily devouring a meal."


translate English day1_hakuB__18816fba:


    "Whatever the case, it certainly doesn't seem to be in use."


translate English day1_hakuB__07178ff8:


    "Scrape... Scrape... I hear the sound of something scratching along the dirt and sand. If that's a mountain beast, I'm in trouble. I hurry and hide myself, then look in the direction I heard it."


translate English day1_hakuB__5377aa36:


    "Surprisingly, as my eyes turn that way, I see a person standing there alone. There's no mistaking it--"


translate English day1_hakuB__61c7a02f:


    et "not considering the utterly black night sky and the pure white light radiating from them."


translate English day1_hakuB__76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day1_hakuB__63875b49:


    "\n The person has white hair, neatly tied at the back. They wear a rose corsage in it."


translate English day1_hakuB__a166cea7:


    "The white light is strange and incongruent with the surrounding darkness. Instead of lurking within it, it controls the space around it, drawing the attention of any would-be viewers. I've never met anyone like that before."


translate English day1_hakuB__13a42c99:


    "But their expression is so cold that I have trouble feeling regular human goodwill toward them."


translate English day1_hakuB__d5cc5675:


